# Build-copy targets when ModsPath resolves to project-relative (e.g. a build
# invoked with an empty /p:ModsPath= flag). The csproj's CopyToModsFolderOnBuild
# target drops the built DLL + manifest + fonts into $(ModsPath)SlayTheStats/
# and BaseLib files into $(ModsPath)BaseLib/. mod_image.png inside
# SlayTheStats/SlayTheStats/ is a tracked source asset and stays.
